The Telegraph - Calcutta (Kolkata) | Metro | Good Morning
                                                                                                                         3                                                                                      Good Morning
      Hello It's Friday , November 12 , 2010                    
	Roads to avoid    St Georges Gate Road, Kingway, Red Road, Mayo Road, Strand Road, Bagbazar Street, SN Banerjee Road and other roads leading to bathing ghats along the Hooghly because of Chhat Puja, from afternoon.    
	Events    The Puffin Quiz 2010 with Derek OBrien, at South City School, 9am.    Yeh Image Mahaan: India Meets Bharat, at CIMA Gallery, 11am to 7pm.    Preview of Ecriture III... and a few other things at Akar Prakar, 6.30pm.    An exhibition of paintings by Tilok Mandal and Sudip Banerjee at Academy of Fine Arts (New South Gallery A), 3pm to 8pm.    A health and yoga workshop for expectant mothers at Golds Gym, 57 JL Nehru Road, 10am to 7pm.                                                                                                                                                  
